    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><strong>Student Support</strong></p>
<p>Student support is the responsibility of the partner institution. Support should be equivalent to that provided by QMU. This should include:</p>
<ul>
<li>A named contact for students to approach with any academic or personal problems (at QMU this is the Personal Academic Tutor).</li>
<li>Procedures for providing support with learning disabilities such as dyslexia and dyspraxia.</li>
<li>Procedures for supporting students with key academic skills such as referencing, academic writing, IT, spelling and grammar.</li>
<li>Support for English language (for students whose first language is not English)</li>
<li>Arrangements for personal development planning.</li>
<li>Support for students from the full range of diverse backgrounds.</li>
<li>Provision of careers advice.</li>
</ul>]]></Value>
    </introduction>
